90d38ffe0d4a27eff005375a4453ce58","tid":103410,"uid":20385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T10:46:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點解好多紅van司機都好惡"},{"pid":"924491513010b9bb3517d51d2c7d1f312111eca4","tid":103410,"uid":1773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T10:46:57.000Z","msg":"Jony的紅VAN車頭印有「阿拉真神」的文字。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25ee01c496a07a3f3fa27b29153183b0da74c843","tid":103410,"uid":35420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T10:47:37.000Z","msg":"佢本身都幾有米喎又用30萬裝修又買起架紅van"},{"pid":"05b716676c547c3d16f182f42ae7a66195780a46","tid":103410,"uid":41821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T10:47:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>入線費,埋站費係撚司機比咩</blockquote><br />\n架車佢自己買左</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔怪得車頭印左阿拉啦"},{"pid":"1b8ce520c72aa58a605cb05c0469e1e1a77eb0a0","tid":103410,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T10:49:14.000Z","msg":"「人哋煮咖喱好食就話開餐廳唧，我都唔識煮嘢食。」即使花了30多萬元裝修，Jony也決定結業。<br />\n<br />\n開過餐廳做老細, 應該有小小家底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b06fb34ce47d149e43eb31df0cf5df858b35f98","tid":103410,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T10:50:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Jony的紅VAN車頭印有「阿拉真神」的文字。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係歐洲<br />\n<br />\n有D恐怖份子 會渣車衝去人群, 發動恐襲<br />\n<br />\n如果佢呢間車係歐洲行, 會唔會比人誤當係恐怖份子 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8496af235af420c1587f4442235e8084a06ba012","tid":103410,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T10:51:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>搭過佢部車，手車都幾危險，下車要急急落，唔係夾死你<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申一星期搭五日，屌佢老母紅van愈黎愈貴，架車愈黎愈殘</blockquote><br />\n屌車主（馬亞木）la<