hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你估係果架紅van咩<br />\n過完隧道就穿越去左歐洲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/02/012614_4b90d15c65b43f13d5874df31919e33a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F02%2F012614_4b90d15c65b43f13d5874df31919e33a.jpg&h=7b04fca7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0d3e5f8102a381455fe706f62a6a0b400f2a7a44","tid":103410,"uid":49678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T17:26:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我做野個頭其實都好多少數族裔既人，可悲既係有啲高學歷既都搵唔到野做，好多都要去做厭惡性工作例如倒垃圾個啲，如果香港人唔歧視佢地其實未必會有咁多人犯案</blockquote><br />\n人必自侮而後人侮之<br />\n內文都有講好多南亞人比中介人呃錢,搵唔到野做選擇犯案,D人先開始歧視佢地<br />\n點解你會講到係香港人搞到佢地犯案?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n僧多粥少，本地人都有高學歷但要做低學歷工作啦，乜都講到係香港責任咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a453aa4a47fbf032df21c152f5e23f29d292b662","tid":103410,"uid":15984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T17:27:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我搭過 佢手車超好 轉波唔chok又快 十分鐘到富佑 不過當然係深夜先有咁既速度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n帶好多人等佢果架先搭"},{"pid":"9d03a06bae157061a4041b91795bb7eada050bc6","tid":103410,"uid":33653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T17:35:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Jony的紅VAN車頭印有「阿拉真神」的文字。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係歐洲<br />\n<br />\n有D恐怖份子 會渣車衝去人群, 發動恐襲<br />\n<br />\n如果佢呢間車係歐洲行, 會唔會比人誤當係恐怖份子 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </blockquote><br />\n你估係果架紅van咩<br />\n過完隧道就穿越去左歐洲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/02/012614_4b90d15c65b43f13d5874df31919e33a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F02%2F012614_4b90d15c65b43f13d5874df31919e33a.jpg&h=7b04fca7&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港換曬石油氣，柴油版無人要。"},{"pid":"a607fbeaed538281d438c577f9c38bb72124c590","tid":103410,"uid":20809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T17:38:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實點解要俾幾十萬入線費？</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你咪試下唔俾<br />\n可能一個月維修費用都幾十萬</blockquote><br />\n條友升到中學未 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你地俾人欺凌慣？入線費係政府費用黎架？真係未撚聽過咩部門咁撚巴閉。<br />\n屌你老母你班傻閪選擇妥協唔代表呢樣野係岩，我梗係知唔俾就會有班垃圾黑社會搞佢架車，咁就代表岩？<br />\n呢d同勒索有咩分別<br />\n<br />\n你呢d傻閪如果話你老細想執你老母一劑先俾你繼續打工，仲話&quot;行規黎架，個個老母都俾我咁屌&quot;,我諗你都會雙手奉上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74874f57d8c13f679de3d84e57d3b2c42487f53f","tid":103410,"uid":20362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T17:43:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你咪試下唔俾<br />\n可能一個月維修費用都幾十萬</blockquote><br />\n條友升到中學未 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你地俾人欺凌慣？入線費係政府費用黎架？真係未撚聽過咩部門咁撚巴閉。<br />\n屌你老母你班傻閪選擇妥協唔代表呢樣野係岩，我梗係知唔俾就會有班垃圾黑社會搞佢架車，咁就代表岩？<br />\n呢d同勒索有咩分別<br />\n<br />\n你呢d傻閪如果話你老細想執你老母一劑先俾你繼續打工，仲話&quot;行規黎架，個個老母都俾我咁屌&quot;,我諗你都會雙手奉上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁借問聲你除左比仲可以點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f68ed3b59a6d354d7c4af34ddc07775b3d4db7b5","tid":103410,"uid":58209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T17:43:59.000Z","msg":"前幾日搭完先發覺又加左1蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n明明新搬黎慈雲山果時先6蚊<br />\n依家大拿拿10蚊呀，屌你老母<img src=\"/ass