 />\n你唔諗下而家幾多人無野做"},{"pid":"a70c8bd7ecc176beef5b07617d424389da83d81d","tid":103410,"uid":21222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T18:57:32.000Z","msg":"一年學識廣東省話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 蝗住夠7年都唔識講"},{"pid":"512cc4e0958e8a42f474f1bb6c9dccd18f6f74c8","tid":103410,"uid":81569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T19:36:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你咪試下唔俾<br />\n可能一個月維修費用都幾十萬</blockquote><br />\n條友升到中學未 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你地俾人欺凌慣？入線費係政府費用黎架？真係未撚聽過咩部門咁撚巴閉。<br />\n屌你老母你班傻閪選擇妥協唔代表呢樣野係岩，我梗係知唔俾就會有班垃圾黑社會搞佢架車，咁就代表岩？<br />\n呢d同勒索有咩分別<br />\n<br />\n你呢d傻閪如果話你老細想執你老母一劑先俾你繼續打工，仲話&quot;行規黎架，個個老母都俾我咁屌&quot;,我諗你都會雙手奉上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁借問聲你除左比仲可以點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我表叔開左廿幾年紅van<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一直都唔比<br />\n到呢家都冇比人搞過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都好奇怪<br />\n明明佢普通市民一個<br />\n利申:親眼見過佢同d旺角肥佬講 唔會交數"},{"pid":"540def3950d4c13f5d6ea874cbdd7a526f6f5072","tid":103410,"uid":27605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T20:05:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n你地俾人欺凌慣？入線費係政府費用黎架？真係未撚聽過咩部門咁撚巴閉。<br />\n屌你老母你班傻閪選擇妥協唔代表呢樣野係岩，我梗係知唔俾就會有班垃圾黑社會搞佢架車，咁就代表岩？<br />\n呢d同勒索有咩分別<br />\n<br />\n你呢d傻閪如果話你老細想執你老母一劑先俾你繼續打工，仲話&quot;行規黎架，個個老母都俾我咁屌&quot;,我諗你都會雙手奉上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁借問聲你除左比仲可以點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我表叔開左廿幾年紅van<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一直都唔比<br />\n到呢家都冇比人搞過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都好奇怪<br />\n明明佢普通市民一個<br />\n利申:親眼見過佢同d旺角肥佬講 唔會交數</blockquote><br />\n唔入線就要拎白牌 <br />\n唔可以係站頭排隊 淨係可以走圍兜 比人見到你係佢地既站頭上客 輕則屌你一獲 重則扑爆玻璃打你一身<br />\n之前hk01有講"},{"pid":"fe9236817cfb0bb5d9fa1958b940ed15e18d1120","tid":103410,"uid":27605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T20:10:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實點解要俾幾十萬入線費？</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你咪試下唔俾<br />\n可能一個月維修費用都幾十萬</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n垃圾黑社會<br />\n有破壞冇建設，其實同新移民有咩分別 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但政府可以點解決 嚴打黑社會既話 突然幾萬個無飯開走出黎搞事 又要比你地屌 壓抑算啦 黑社會都無以前咁惡啦"},{"pid":"389b6f510399c0a354e076a1bb8c771487531fa0","tid":103410,"uid":3295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T20:33:02.000Z","msg":"點解個阿拉真神可以寫到咁有老mk風味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98193a10440c9514d548ea84aab4bb9a5db51faf","tid":103410,"uid":16676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T20:38:09.000Z","msg":"專屬van 仔站牌 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n前一排先吹奏完果個寫站牌佬<br />\n<br />\n原來佢地係一幫人, 所以獨市<br />\n<br />\n條友仲話有自己版權<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實講到尾係同班黑社會同一伙搵錢<br />\n<br />\n果時上報已經心諗, 呢d 咁既站牌間間賣膠片既舖頭想做既實做到架嘛<br />\n<br />\n而家個個都識用電腦, 自製, 度身訂造有幾難喎<br />\n<br />\n點會獨市架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔怪得佢賺撚到盤滿砵滿仲上報紙添啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n原來<span style=\"color: red;\">大家雙方面都咁嘿嘿 </span><br />\n<br />\n每個司機要比十幾個先有塊膠牌用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d69f0408c93b19af61e24a79a9a65fa7f8463122","tid":103410,"uid":9564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T23:36:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>依啲呀差先值得人尊敬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n不過連登都有好大堆唔會理佢係咪好人，見人係南亞既就分分鐘想佢撞車死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唉"},{"pid":"c02b6e855a7e4c2b9fbf031b40e0da2268b715dd","tid":103410,"uid":8572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T23:55:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>搭過佢部車，手車都幾危險，落車要急急落，唔係夾死你<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申一星期搭五日，屌佢老母紅van愈黎愈貴，架車愈黎愈殘</blockquote><br />\n去九番十<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d4729e70bd25c6d692760b0ae67f5e5203d1dc8","tid":103410,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T06:58:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實點解要俾幾十萬入線費？</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你咪試下唔俾<br />\n可能一個月維修費用都幾十萬</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n垃圾黑社會<br />\n有破壞冇建設，其實同新移民有咩分別 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但政府可以點解決 嚴打黑社會既話 突然幾萬個無飯開走出黎搞事 又要比你地屌 壓抑算啦 黑社會都無以前咁惡啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n學希特拉, 墨索里尼 咁<br />\n<br />\n幾萬個黑社會 走出來話無飯食, 全部捉去處決"},{"pid":"2fd6af56be7658e7738811f4255d10077c9e5c3b","tid":103410,"uid":81569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T08:01:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實點解要俾幾十萬入線費？</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你咪試下唔俾<br />\n可能一個月維修費用都幾十萬</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n垃圾黑社會<br />\n有破壞冇建設，其實同新移民有咩